at budskap p\u00e5 dem.<\/p>\n<h3>Skr\u00e4ddarsydda och s\u00e4kert monterade<\/h3>\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Korgmarkiserna fr\u00e5n Bellevue Solskydd \u00e4r ett \u00e4kta hantverk. Du v\u00e4ljer fast eller f\u00e4llbar korg, f\u00e4rg och m\u00f6nster p\u00e5 den h\u00e5llbara och v\u00e4dert\u00e5liga v\u00e4ven. Sedan tillverkar vi markiserna, helt efter m\u00e5tten p\u00e5 varje f\u00f6nster. I priset kan montering erbjudas och utf\u00f6rs d\u00e5 av v\u00e5ra specialister.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/kostnadsfritt-hembesok-BTN.png&#8221; title_text=&#8221;kostnadsfritt hembeso\u0308k- BTN&#8221; url=&#8221;\/#hembasok\/&#8221; show_bottom_space=&#8221;off&#8221; align=&#8221;right&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.1&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; transform_translate=&#8221;30px|0px&#8221; transform_translate_linked=&#8221;off&#8221; transform_rotate=&#8221;0deg|0deg|10deg&#8221; position_origin_a=&#8221;center_center&#8221; position_origin_r=&#8221;bottom_right&#8221; width=&#8221;150px&#8221; width_tablet=&#8221;150px&#8221; width_phone=&#8221;120px&#8221; width_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;40px||||false|false&#8221; custom_margin_tablet=&#8221;0px||||false|false&#8221; custom_margin_phone=&#8221;0px||||false|false&#8221; custom_margin_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; animation_style=&#8221;slide&#8221; animation_direction=&#8221;right&#8221; animation_duration=&#8221;1500ms&#8221; animation_intensity_slide=&#8221;30%&#8221; border_radii=&#8221;on|10px|10px|10px|10px&#8221; box_shadow_style=&#8221;preset3&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; transform_styles__hover_enabled=&#8221;on|hover&#8221; transform_scale__hover_enabled=&#8221;on|hover&#8221; transform_tr